The paper discusses the growth of citations to old documents, which is a topic related to digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The study also involves analyzing data and using statistical measures, which falls under the category of computational complexity (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses the possible causes of the phenomenon, which could be related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and social networks (cs.SI).
